 class ChiSquareDistribution
          chi-square distribution (distribution of sum of squares of n N(0,1) random variables)

(Parameter: n; mean: n; variance: 2*n)

The chi-square distribution is a special case of the Gamma distribution (shape parameter = n/2.0, scale = 2.0).
